          <text>
                    <body>
                              <pb n="1"/>
                              <p rend="align(right)">
                                        <placeName>Barcelona</placeName>
                                        <date>Decr. 9<hi rend="sup">th</hi> 1853</date>
                              </p>
                              <p rend="indent(1)">
                                        <addressee>Is. Leeser Esqr.</addressee>
                              </p>
                              <p rend="indent(2)">
                                        <placeName>Philadpa.</placeName>
                              </p>
                              <p rend="indent(4)">Revd. Sir</p>
                              <p rend="indent(3)">As I am about retiring from this part of
                                                  <placeName>America</placeName><lb/> during the
                                        ensuing month of <date>Janry.</date>, I must beg you to
                                        hasten<lb/> the remittance of the Books ordered &amp; at the
                                        same time request<lb/> you to draw at <hi rend="underline"
                                                  >eight days</hi> sight for their import, in favor of<lb/>
                                        <persName>Messrs A. M. Seixas &amp; Co.</persName> of
                                                  <placeName>LaGuaira</placeName>. Please send also
                                        the<lb/> bill of their <sic>seperate</sic> costs.</p>
                              <p rend="indent(3)">Your last letter reached me just on the point
                                        of<lb/> Leaving this for
                                                  <placeName><sic>curacao</sic></placeName> &amp;
                                        was extremely sorry that it also reached<lb/> me so late in
                                        the season &amp; thereby preventing me from remitting<lb/>
                                        you the <add>Hebrew</add> asked for; but should your
                                        expected letter arrive<lb/> in time &amp; should you still
                                        required them, I shall then endeavor<lb/> in time &amp;
                                        should you still require them, I shall then endeavor<lb/>
                                        forward you some either by way of
                                                  <placeName>LaGuaira</placeName>, <placeName>St
                                                  Thos</placeName> or direct.</p>
                              <p rend="indent(8)">In haste I remain Revd Sir</p>
                              <p rend="indent(9)">
                                        <persName role="author">Saml Piza</persName>
                              </p>
                              <p>PS. Please include the amt. I owe for the Occident in the bill<lb/>
                                        drawn in favor of <persName>Messrs A. M Seixas &amp;
                                                  Co.</persName> &amp; cease sending after the<lb/>
                                        month. <hi rend="underline">vale</hi></p>
                              <pb n="2"/>
                              <p>Forwarded by <persName>D <add>?</add> S</persName></p>
                    </body>
